sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Host page
    participant C as Componente embutivel
    participant X as layout-mestre-api.js
    participant K as PayloadCrypto
    participant API as Backend

    H->>C: definirYaml / setUserEmail / setApiKey / setMode
    C->>X: enviar(modo, conteudo)
    X->>K: buildEncryptedData(yaml)
    K->>API: POST /crypto/session-key
    API-->>K: session_id + public_key_pem
    K-->>X: encrypted_data
    X->>API: POST /rag|"/agent"|/workflow/execute (X-API-Key, encrypted_data)
    API-->>X: 200 sincrono ou 202 assincrono + X-Correlation-Id
    alt assincrono
        loop ate status terminal
            X->>API: GET /api/v1/status/{task_id} (X-API-Key)
            API-->>X: status, percentage, result?, error?
        end
    end
    X-->>C: resultado normalizado + correlation_id
    C-->>H: evento response-received / error
